  "instructions": [
    "Press tofu to remove excess water for 10 minutes then cube.",
    "Whisk soy sauce, yuzu zest, yuzu juice, liquid smoke, tahini, water, salt, and pepper until smooth.",
    "Add tofu cubes to the sauce and let marinate for 15 minutes.",
    "Heat a skillet over medium heat and stir-fry tofu for 5-7 minutes until golden and firm.",
    "Transfer tofu to a molcajete and crush lightly with a pestle to release briny juices.",
    "Arrange cucumber, carrot, and spinach on a plate.",
    "Spoon tofu mixture over vegetables and sprinkle toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Drizzle a little extra yuzu juice for brightness.",
    "Serve immediately while warm."
